We may collect information about your computer and basic google analytics such as website visits. We will not collect any personal information, only analytics for statistical purposes. Some games on this website may collect information in game that will be sent to the developers of the respective game for advertising or other purposes. We will not be held responsible for any privacy practices on their end. Any personal information that you provide to our website will not be disclosed to any third-party sites.
